Indian language TrueType fonts for Windows

The following links point to sources of Indian language fonts that can be downloaded and installed in Windows.

    TDIL Hindi Fonts and more... (http://ildc.gov.in/hindi/hdownloadhindi.htm)
    TDIL Telugu Fonts (http://ildc.gov.in/telugu/tdownload2k.htm)
    TDIL Kannada Fonts (http://ildc.gov.in/Kannada/kdownload2k.htm)
    TDIL Tamil Fonts (http://www.ildc.in/GIST/htm/fonts.htm)
    Several other TDIL Unicode Fonts (http://ildc.gov.in/)
    SALRC, The University of Chicago (http://salrc.uchicago.edu/resources/fonts/available/)
    WAZU JAPAN's Gallery of Unicode Fonts  (http://www.wazu.jp/)
    IndLinux Indic Fonts List (http://indlinux.org/wiki/index.php/IndicFontsList)
